  "title": "Frontend Engineer (React JS)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Proven ability to do Analysis, Development and Test in agile methodology</li><li>4 years of experience working on Front End technologies (Swift or Kotlin or React Native or Java)</li><li>Understand concept working with Javascript (pros and cons of the technology), modular architectures and Micro-Services</li><li>Preferably 1 year of experience with Selenium, not a necessary skill</li><li>Tried at least 1 XP practice</li><li>Experience working with UX designer</li><li>Strong experience on writing Unit tests and UI tests</li><li>Good experience on programming paradigms such as object oriented, functional and reactive</li><li>Experience working with tools Xcode/Android Studio, Webstorm, Jenkins, Artifactory, Sonar, Git</li><li>Experience on Apple and Google Design Guidelines</li><li>Experience with dependency management tools such cocoapods or gradle is must</li><li>Sound knowledge on various encryption algorithms is required</li><li>Should have strong problem solving capabilities.</li><li>Strong knowledge on Unit testing</li><li>Understanding of code documentation</li></ul>",
